---
// Layout Import
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
// Component Imports
import { Markdown } from 'astro/components';

// Data Fetching: List all Markdown posts in the repo.
let allPosts = Astro.fetchContent('./posts/*.md');
allPosts = allPosts.sort((a, b) => new Date(b.date) - new Date(a.date));
---
<MainLayout title="About Me" description="Here's a quick summary..." head={
  <>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/flickity@2/dist/flickity.min.css">
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/flickity@2/dist/flickity.pkgd.min.js"></script>
    <script>
      document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
        const carouselEl = document.querySelector('.about-carousel');
        const carousel = new Flickity( carouselEl, {
          autoPlay: true,
          percentPosition: false,
          wrapAround: true,
          resize: true,
          lazyLoad: 2,
        });
      })
    </script>
  </>
}>
    <div class="about-carousel">
      <img 
        src="https://assets.codepen.io/1490503/mykal-6.jpg?width=16&height=18&format=auto" 
        data-flickity-lazyload="https://assets.codepen.io/1490503/mykal-6.jpg?format=auto" 
        alt="Mykal drinking a coffee in Vancouver" />
      <img 
        src="https://assets.codepen.io/1490503/mykal_and_dad.jpg?width=118&height=88&format=auto" 
        data-flickity-lazyload="https://assets.codepen.io/1490503/mykal_and_dad.jpg?width=709&height=531&format=auto" 
        alt="Mykal and his dad biking in Vancouver on the sea wall" />
      <img 
        src="https://assets.codepen.io/1490503/mykal_alt.jpg?width=151&height=201&format=auto"
        data-flickity-lazyload="https://assets.codepen.io/1490503/mykal_alt.jpg?width=756&height=1008&format=auto" 
        alt="Mykal drinking coffee in on the White Rock sea wall" />
      <img 
        src="https://assets.codepen.io/1490503/mykal_4.jpg?width=163&height=122&format=auto" 
        data-flickity-lazyload="https://assets.codepen.io/1490503/mykal_4.jpg?width=816&height=612&format=auto" 
        alt="Kiya and Mykal posing for a selfie in Penticton" />
      <img 
        src="https://assets.codepen.io/1490503/mykal_5.jpg?width=120&height=90&format=auto"
        data-flickity-lazyload="https://assets.codepen.io/1490503/mykal_5.jpg?width=720&height=540&format=auto"
        alt="Kiya and Mykal posing in front of a mural" />
      <img 
        src="https://assets.codepen.io/1490503/mykal_3.jpg?width=59&height=110&format=auto"
        data-flickity-lazyload="https://assets.codepen.io/1490503/mykal_3.jpg?width=712&height=1324&format=auto" 
        alt="Kiya and Mykal pose with their mouths open- there's a snapchat filter that puts turtles on their cheeks">
    </div>
    <i class="caption">pictured above: goofy of pictures of me, cats, and my Fianc√©e Kiya</i>
    <div class="blog-post">
      <Markdown>
        ## Professional
        Professionally, I write software. mostly web, besides that, idk- still figuring it out.
        I have a weird laundry list of technical skills including "modern" web, Shopify theme, and Backend dev. I'll also be picking up some general IT and Enterprise systems knowledge [soon](/posts/starting-at-ufv).
        
        I like learning and solving technical problems, and just sort of follow whatever road that leads me down! _It's worked so far!_

        I also run a small consulting co all by my lonesome, so if you have a problem you want to solve, [check it out!](https://tinybox.dev) 

        ## Personal
        Just another white dude in tech.
        I like spending time with friends, and family (including my 2 cats), and doing general nerd things including: 
        1. Video Games
        2. Building side projects
        3. Touching grass (I like biking!)

        ## Education
        I'm one class away from completing a Bachelor in Computer Information Systems with a major in Software Development; I should graduate in December 2021! 
      </Markdown>
    </div>
</MainLayout>  

